\frac{1}{2+\frac{1}{4+\frac{1}{4+\frac{1}{\ldots}}}}
x
x = \cfrac{1}{2+\cfrac{1}{4+\cfrac{1}{4+\cdots}}}.
x^{-1} = 2 + \cfrac{1}{4+\cfrac{1}{4+\cfrac{1}{4+\cdots}}}.
x^{-1} - 2 = \cfrac{1}{4+\cfrac{1}{4+\cfrac{1}{4+\cdots}}}.
y = \cfrac{1}{4+\cfrac{1}{4+\cfrac{1}{4+\cdots}}}.
y^{-1} = 4 + \cfrac{1}{4+\cfrac{1}{4+\cfrac{1}{4+\cdots}}}.
y^{-1} = 4 + y.
